      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "If you still feel unwell after the juice and your meter is unreliable, treat the symptoms of low blood sugar until you can get a proper reading. Since you feel weird and dizzy, assume a low and stick to the 15-15 rule: eat 15g of carbs, wait 15 minutes, and check your glucose again. Do not dose insulin based on a hunch; focus on raising your blood sugar safely first.",
      "source": "target",
